message: Hi Bob, I'm selling this amazing product that I think you'd be interested in. I'm asking for $10000 for it.  Let me know what you think!
Thanks for the offer, Alice! That's a great starting point. I'm interested, but I'm only able to go up to $9000 right now.  Let me know what you think.
Thanks for the counteroffer, Bob. I appreciate your interest!  I'm willing to come down to $9500. This is a great deal for a product of this quality. Let me know what you think.
